[package]
name = "bevy_egui"
version = "0.33.0"
rust-version = "1.80.0"
authors = [ "vladbat00 <vladyslav.batyrenko@gmail.com>",]
description = "A plugin for Egui integration into Bevy"
license = "MIT"
edition = "2021"
repository = "https://github.com/vladbat00/bevy_egui"
exclude = [ "assets/**/*", ".github/**/*",]

[features]
default = [ "manage_clipboard", "open_url", "default_fonts", "render",]
immutable_ctx = []
manage_clipboard = [ "arboard", "thread_local", "bytemuck",]
open_url = [ "webbrowser",]
default_fonts = [ "egui/default_fonts",]
render = [ "bevy_asset", "bevy_image", "bevy_picking", "bevy_render", "encase", "bytemuck", "egui/bytemuck", "wgpu-types",]
serde = [ "egui/serde",]
log_input_events = []

[dependencies]
bevy_app = "0.15.0"
bevy_derive = "0.15.0"
bevy_ecs = "0.15.0"
bevy_input = "0.15.0"
bevy_log = "0.15.0"
bevy_math = "0.15.0"
bevy_reflect = "0.15.0"
bevy_time = "0.15.0"
bevy_utils = "0.15.0"
bevy_window = "0.15.0"

[dev-dependencies]
version-sync = "0.9.4"

[dependencies.egui]
version = "0.31"
default-features = false

[dependencies.bevy_winit]
version = "0.15.0"
features = [ "custom_cursor",]

[dependencies.webbrowser]
version = "1.0.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.bytemuck]
version = "1"
optional = true

[dependencies.bevy_asset]
version = "0.15.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.bevy_image]
version = "0.15.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.bevy_picking]
version = "0.15.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.bevy_render]
version = "0.15.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.encase]
version = "0.10"
optional = true

[dependencies.wgpu-types]
version = "23.0"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.bevy]
version = "0.15.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "bevy_asset", "bevy_core_pipeline", "bevy_sprite", "bevy_pbr", "bevy_window", "bevy_winit", "android-game-activity", "png", "tonemapping_luts", "webgl2", "x11",]

[dev-dependencies.egui]
version = "0.31"
default-features = false
features = [ "bytemuck",]

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies]
winit = "0.30"
js-sys = "0.3.63"
wasm-bindgen = "0.2.84"
wasm-bindgen-futures = "0.4.36"
crossbeam-channel = "0.5.8"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "bevy_winit/x11",]
all-features = true

[target."cfg(not(any(target_arch = \"wasm32\", target_os = \"android\")))".dependencies.arboard]
version = "3.2.0"
optional = true

[target."cfg(not(any(target_arch = \"wasm32\", target_os = \"android\")))".dependencies.thread_local]
version = "1.1.0"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.web-sys]
version = "0.3.74"
features = [ "Clipboard", "ClipboardEvent", "ClipboardItem", "CompositionEvent", "DataTransfer", "Document", "EventTarget", "HtmlInputElement", "InputEvent", "KeyboardEvent", "Navigator", "TouchEvent", "Window",]

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.image]
version = "0.25.5"
features = [ "png",]

[[example]]
name = "filtering"
path = "./examples/filtering.rs"

[[example]]
name = "importing"
path = "./examples/importing.rs"

[[example]]
name = "toggle"
path = "./examples/toggle.rs"

[package]
name = "bevy_enum_filter"
version = "0.6.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Gino Valente <gino.valente.code@gmail.com>",]
description = "Filter by enum variant in Bevy queries"
repository = "https://github.com/MrGVSV/bevy_enum_filter"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
keywords = [ "bevy", "enum", "filter", "variant", "query",]
categories = [ "game-development",]
readme = "README.md"
exclude = [ "assets/**/*", ".github/**/*", "screenshots/**/*",]

[dev-dependencies]
bevy = "0.15"

[dependencies.bevy_app]
version = "0.15"
default-features = false

[dependencies.bevy_ecs]
version = "0.15"
default-features = false

[dependencies.bevy_enum_filter_derive]
path = "./bevy_enum_filter_derive"
version = "0.2.0"

[package]
name = "bevy_enum_filter_derive"
version = "0.2.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Gino Valente <gino.valente.code@gmail.com>",]
description = "Derive and helper macros for bevy_enum_filter"
repository = "https://github.com/MrGVSV/bevy_enum_filter"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
keywords = [ "bevy", "enum", "filter", "variant", "query",]
categories = [ "game-development",]

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
syn = "1.0"
proc-macro2 = "1.0"
proc-macro-crate = "1.2"
quote = "1.0"
convert_case = "0.6.0"

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://codeberg.org/terratactician-expandoria/bevy_egui"]
git = "https://codeberg.org/terratactician-expandoria/bevy_egui"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "e22e561b34a8043835182eb6b6220effc5189e95"

[source."https://codeberg.org/terratactician-expandoria/bevy_enum_filter"]

replace-with = "vendored-sources"
